queries.sql: SELECT `tbl_tickets`.*, `u1`.`nombre` AS `nombre_usuario`, `u2`.`nombre` AS `nombre_cliente`, `tbl_areas`.`nombre` AS `nombre_area`, IFNULL(tbl_sla.color, "") AS color_sla, (SELECT ruta FROM tbl_documentos_tickets d WHERE d.ticket_id = tbl_tickets.id ORDER BY fecha_subida DESC LIMIT 1) AS url FROM `tbl_tickets` LEFT JOIN `tbl_usuarios` AS `u1` ON `tbl_tickets`.`usuario_id` = `u1`.`id` LEFT JOIN `tbl_usuarios` AS `u2` ON `tbl_tickets`.`cliente_id` = `u2`.`id` LEFT JOIN `tbl_areas` ON `tbl_tickets`.`area_id` = `tbl_areas`.`id` LEFT JOIN `tbl_sla` ON `tbl_tickets`.`prioridad` = `tbl_sla`.`titulo` ORDER BY `tbl_tickets`.`id` DESC
